{"tid":1461377,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急] 機場一戰好關鍵，但要提防政府陰招！!","createTime":"2019-08-13T07:29:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T21:06:13.000Z","uid":288917,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c61f43cd40170954b1a7e80db477789ba645fde5","tid":1461377,"uid":288917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:29:05.000Z","msg":"話說我尋日去送朋友機，但去到已經發現唔駛飛。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktW4H9x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktW4H9x.jpg&h=4c0c26eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當時無限流傳嘅 速龍清場，停機鐵，熄燈 fake資訊都算喇。<br />\n奇怪嘅係，點解離港(departure)航班會咁快咁容易就一律cancel晒?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pJjqsBQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpJjqsBQ.jpg&h=b15c1f08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但到港(arrival)航班就大部分都正常？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lmd6Wvf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLmd6Wvf.jpg&h=5253305e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果 政府/民航處 真係覺得機場對旅客有危險，點解唔cancel埋到港航班，轉飛鄰近機場？ 離境大堂雖然係多人，但其實完全冇阻礙旅客check-in。<br />\n<br />\n客觀睇返政府近期嘅陰濕行為，有理由相信可能又係政府設嘅局。目的可能有幾個：<br />\n1) 令大量旅客滯留產生亂局，甚至打鬥，跟住推晒責任落抗爭者身上。（呢個可以解釋點解剩係cancel departure）<br />\n2) 嘗試用勝利沖昏大家嘅頭腦。<br />\n3) 又玩乜乜乜影響經濟/旅遊業 嘗試扭轉民意。<br />\n<br />\n尋日政府 喺第1點明顯係失敗嘅，因為冇阻礙旅客check-in，而且手足都好有禮貌咁解釋香港實況。但呢點仍然好重要，對離港旅客文宣絕對唔可以忽視。第2點就唔多講喇，只係想講太容易得到嘅嘢通常都有伏。第3點 基本上政府就一定會咁玩㗎啦，我地最緊要係唔好畀佢轉移視線，要多方面將問題原頭指返政府，並且借旅客對外傳播始作佣者係政府，cancel 航班亦係政府。<br />\n<br />\n要繼續食住機場，大家就要緊慎行事!  唔好畀政府有任何機會!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd618dfd19f844b541abda55a721729b7c072b2","tid":1461377,"uid":277084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:29:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"122e794013654c96a0a6543a62acb5a4423ac95d","tid":1461377,"uid":109820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:29:50.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n【推出去】對付五毛好方法<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1461318\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1461318</a>"},{"pid":"f4da37fda38f69aa834a0dfdeba5731b6e699ed3","tid":1461377,"uid":130698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:30:29.000Z","msg":"---------離線通訊神器---------<br />\nAndroid 版Airdrop：Files by Google<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1457044\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1457044</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Google Play: Files by Google 連結</strong> <a href=\"https://g.co/filesgo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fg.co%2Ffilesgo&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDb2ztmS%2FM%2FHF6fRawSWcCn68%3D&h=59b16766\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://g.co/filesgo</a>"},{"pid":"d646529bdc51250c49797d581edad7789f66a7b5","tid":1461377,"uid":288917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:32:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f9e68a1e13a975ed8e042f7cb0c6085918f531b9","tid":1461377,"uid":288917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:35:51.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"e92745a24ed7437fee2c32f088b33f1889c10c6d","tid":1461377,"uid":288917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:39:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"758966cff29db08f8431ad769edb11d15b4bbc01","tid":1461377,"uid":288917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:46:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"bf2fe20d14ce9ab0ed32779f83f6c6092c26f907","tid":1461377,"uid":288917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:04:24.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"1b3e50b3719d81ddd0fa47d91a858a9be3fb6773","tid":1461377,"uid":231641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:58:53.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"12148c30d3abd4556a699c782ad75e7de635eb84","tid":1461377,"uid":60941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:00:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bac6c58b8